metadata.name: In My Head
metadata.description:
The first Jackintheway NFT ever minted.

Collector will receive & experience:*  
- Private thank you chat with Jack over Zoom or Discord  
- Custom 1/1 "In My Head" physical hoodie, embroidered name  
- Secret preview link to listen to the upcoming full-length album  
- Two VIP passes to the album release show (in Washington, DC)  
- Token verified roles & channels in the Wayspace Discord server  
- Access to exclusive IRL & URL events, sessions & listening parties

*Please allow 4-8 weeks for manufacturing and shipping of custom hoodie. Preview link will reflect the current state of the album. Any scheduled event opportunities are subject to change.
